      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Peter Fendrich</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:167px;\"><a href=\"/File:Jean-Peter_Fendrich_3.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/e/e8/Jean-Peter_Fendrich_3.jpg\" width=\"165\" height=\"243\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Jean-Peter_Fendrich_3.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Peter Fendrich <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jean-Peter Fendrich</b>,<br />\na Swedish engineer, computer scientist, in 2014 retired from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volvo\">Volvo</a> IT <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. As avocational computer chess programmer, Peter Fendrich is author of the computer chess programs <a href=\"/Terra\" title=\"Terra\">Terra</a> and <a href=\"/Alaric\" title=\"Alaric\">Alaric</a>.  \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998  ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Fendrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998  ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Fendrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=17016\">Quiescence vs swapoff</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 15, 1998 &#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a>, <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=17377\">Rotated bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 22, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Rotated_Bitboards\" title=\"Rotated Bitboards\">Rotated Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=18821\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 18, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Enhanced_Transposition_Cutoff\" title=\"Enhanced Transposition Cutoff\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=19827\">During Null Move search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 02, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=25091\">Bean counters Part1</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Population_Count\" title=\"Population Count\">Population Count</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=25095\">Bean counters Part2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 1998</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Fendrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=143776\">Q: Fail High percentage</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=311272\">Hash and first Fail High</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 14, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=171#p462\">Re: Attack table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 06, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Attack_and_Defend_Maps\" title=\"Attack and Defend Maps\">Attack and Defend Maps</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=401974\">Temporal Differences</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Fendrich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Temporal_Difference_Learning\" title=\"Temporal Difference Learning\">Temporal Difference Learning</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Fendrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://se.linkedin.com/in/jpfendrich\">Jean-Peter Fendrich | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://terra.fendrich.se/index.html\">Terra Help and Information</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://alaric.fendrich.se/\">Alaric Home</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://alaricblog.fendrich.se/#home\">Alaric Blog</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Fendrich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Image clipped from Peter Fendrich former Volvo IT page, Sociala media och en etablerad verksamhet, April 04, 2010</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://se.linkedin.com/in/jpfendrich\">Jean-Peter Fendrich | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228191120\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5132-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228191120 and revision id 10360\n -->\n"
